  "description": "Facetlock Store serves as the secured storage annex of the Sixfold Cask, set within a narrow wedge aligned to the tavern’s six-faceted geometry. Dark composite shelving rises in strict, repeating cells, each bay banded with luminous linework that records inventory as a continuous geometric script. Prismatic glass panels admit the port’s angular radiance in thin planes, turning stacked casks and sealed crates into hard-edged silhouettes. The floor is voidstone scored with regulated paths that guide load placement and damp the vibration transmitted from the mooring spines.",
